        <caption>
          <p>Distances between measures from external datasets. Comparison of the measures (accuracy, FDR, precision, sensitivity, and specificity) obtained under different cutoffs of VGAC (viral genome assembly coverage) with the measures obtained for the identification of replicases under the 80/80 schema. Comparison was carried out in terms of the distance between the measures according to “Materials and methods.” For a detailed description refer to <xref rid="TS10" ref-type="supplementary-material">Supplementary Table 10</xref>.</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="fmicb-13-967021-g006" position="float"/>
